00:21:58.870 --> 00:21:59.828
Doesn't have to be CEO.

00:21:59.828 --> 00:22:01.424
Could be division,
what have you.

00:22:01.424 --> 00:22:02.840
What are the odds
that they're not

00:22:02.840 --> 00:22:06.890
going to have to fire anybody
from the direct reports?

00:22:06.890 --> 00:22:08.790
JACK WELCH: We bought
two medical companies

00:22:08.790 --> 00:22:14.120
in high growth industries
that were underfunded,

00:22:14.120 --> 00:22:16.060
