biggest business opportunity

00:50:25.570 --> 00:50:26.319
out there?

00:50:26.319 --> 00:50:28.610
What's the biggest, most
exciting thing on the horizon?

00:50:28.610 --> 00:50:32.682
And not at a high level, like
online learning, or digital,

00:50:32.682 --> 00:50:33.640
or something like that.

00:50:33.640 --> 00:50:38.620
But if you were starting out,
what industry would you go in?

00:50:38.620 --> 00:50:39.870
What problem would you tackle?

00:50:39.870 --> 00:50:40.837
What would you do?

00:50:40.837 --> 00:50:41.920
JACK WELCH: You want a go?

00:50:41.920 --> 00:50:44.349
SUZY WELCH: I think
that's one for you.

00:50:44.349 --> 00:50:45.140
I can do one thing.

00:50:45.140 --> 00:50:45.660
I can write.

00:50:45.660 --> 00:50:48.460
So for me, it's like the world
doesn't need that many more

00:50:48.460 --> 00:50:50.946
writers.

00:50:50.946 --> 00:50:52.320
JACK WELCH: Well,
I think biotech

00:50:52.320 --> 00:50:54.640
is just the most exciting
area in the world right now.

00:50:54.640 --> 00:50:55.710
LASZLO BOCK: Why's that?

00:50:55.710 --> 00:50:57.126
JACK WELCH: Because
you're dealing

00:50:57.126 --> 00:50:58.950
with a clear-cut mission.

00:50:58.950 --> 00:51:00.300
You've got one mission.

00:51:00.300 --> 00:51:01.660
It's easy.

00:51:01.660 --> 00:51:04.670
Now, we have a medical
system business in GE.

00:51:04.670 --> 00:51:06.090
We buy medical companies.

00:51:06.090 --> 00:51:08.400
It's not a problem getting
the mission understood

00:51:08.400 --> 00:51:10.110
by everybody.

00:51:10.110 --> 00:51:11.620
You're changing lives.

00:51:11.620 --> 00:51:12.760
You're making lives better.

00:51:12.760 --> 00:51:14.956
You're doing all that.

00:51:14.956 --> 00:51:20.167
I think it's a frontier now
with enormous upside to explore.

00:51:20.167 --> 00:51:21.750
LASZLO BOCK: But
people have said this

00:51:21.750 --> 00:51:23.800
about biotech, like 10
years ago, 20 years ago.

00:51:23.800 --> 00:51:25.020
Is it different
today than it was?

00:51:25.020 --> 00:51:26.603
JACK WELCH: Yes,
it's much hotter now.

00:51:26.603 --> 00:51:27.940
There's much more breakthroughs.

00:51:27.940 --> 00:51:32.470
Drugs are coming out much
faster through technology.

00:51:32.470 --> 00:51:33.350
LASZLO BOCK: Yeah.

00:51:33.350 --> 00:51:35.370
What about-- well,
